OL,7,Fa licence fee increase which was lower
OL,8,Fthan anticipated and which will
OL,9,Finevitably lead to more cuts and
OL,10,Fsavings.
OL,12,FThere is also the question of the
OL,13,Flicence fee itself ` can it be
