OL,6,FIn all of these areas there are some
OL,7,Fgreat successes to celebrate, areas
OL,8,Fwhere there can be legitimate
OL,9,Fdiscussion about how things are going
OL,10,Fand fields where there can be
OL,11,Fimprovements.
OL,13,FBut without a healthy income, overall
OL,14,Fimprovements are hard if not
OL,15,Fimpossible.
