OL,3,CCreative debate required on future of
OL,4,CBBC
OL,6,FShould the BBC focus on providing
OL,7,Ffewer services but making sure they
OL,8,Fare all absolutely top quality? Put
OL,9,Fthe focus principally on the iPlayer,
OL,10,Fthe major linear TV and radio services
OL,11,Fand news? Or are plans to ditch BBC
OL,12,FFour and Radio 4 Extra as linear
OL,13,Fservices misplaced or still ahead of
OL,14,Ftheir time?
OL,16,FWe need to have a creative debate
OL,17,Fabout just what the BBC is for. And
OL,18,Fthis should involve the public ` not
OL,19,Fjust politicians and media types.
